data.description: Welcome to your new home! This charming 2-story residence is nestled on a peaceful cul-de-sac, and enjoys easy access to schools, parks, shopping, and dining options. There have been numerous upgrades to include a recently installed roof and windows, offering reliability for years to come! Upon entering, you will be greeted by a spacious and inviting interior filled with natural light. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, promoting a sense of togetherness. Your well-appointed kitchen features modern appliances, ample cabinetry, and a center island. Upstairs, you’ll discover a generous master suite complete with an en-suite bathroom. The luxurious soaker tub, separate shower and dual sinks create a spa-like experience in the comfort of your own home! Additionally, the sellers are generously providing a carpet allowance. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your new home. Contact us today to schedule a viewing!
